{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"1e0b2131-bee6-479a-881d-818edb55a34b","content":"**Yes, you will hit compatibility issues.** MSTest v3 dropped support for some of your target frameworks:\n\n- **`net5.0`** — ❌ Not supported. MSTest v3 requires .NET 6.0+ (net5.0 reached end-of-life).\n- **`netcoreapp3.1`** — ❌ Not supported. Also EOL and dropped.\n- **`net462`** — ⚠️ Requires at least .NET Framework **4.6.2**, so this one is fine.\n\n### What you need to do\n\nUpdate your `TargetFrameworks` to replace the unsupported TFMs:\n\n| Current | Replacement |\n|---------|-------------|\n| `net5.0` | `net6.0` or `net8.0` |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | `net6.0` or `net8.0` |\n| `net462` | Keep as-is ✅ |\n\nThen upgrade the MSTest packages to v3 (e.g., `3.x`).\n\nWould you like me to apply the migration changes to your project file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b4fe9664-c163-4fbc-8472-b7cfb127d1c6","outputTokens":275,"requestId":"BC21:33166:213224F:24FE35C:69FAA837"},"id":"3b5a7ffb-0e33-44c8-844a-37c035d03cf7","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:32:30.823Z","parentId":"ce974036-a2d6-4e91-b15d-e148612ccbea"}
